data.text:
Submitting items to the Honors list

• Mail: Honors, The Flint Journal, 200 E. First St., Flint, MI 48502

• E-mail: applause@flintjournal.com

• Photos: Unless a self-addressed, stamped envelope is included photos will not be returned.
